Team members:

Each member of the team should fill out the assignment separately and submit to D2L. Make sure to name it with your last name (example: `2.1-assignment-laderas.docx`)

Remember, you can copy plots directly from the app into your word document by right clicking on the plot and choosing "Copy Image" and pasting it into the file.

1. What was your question? (0.5 pts)
1. What variables did you look at? How were they defined? (0.5 pts)
1. Where did you find it in the app? (0.5 pts)
1. What did you expect in terms of the relationship? (1 pts)
1. For another variable, assess the association of it with your non-outcome. (0.5 pts)
1. Did you find a relationship between your variable and outcome? Show the plot that convinced you and write one or two sentences about it. (2 pts)
